name: $consenter
desc: An entity which accepts certain rights or authority from a grantor.

name: $grantee
desc: An entity which agrees to confer certain rights or authority to a grantee.

name: $grantor
desc: A party to whom some right or authority is granted by a delegator.

name: $delegatee
desc: A party that grants all or some portion its right or authority to another party.
